  <section class="card landing-trust-strip" aria-label="Trust highlights">
    <div class="landing-trust-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">What makes switching easy</p>
      <strong>Start with the record you already have.</strong>
    </div>
    <div class="landing-trust-grid">
      <div class="landing-trust-pill">
        <strong>Import old logs</strong>
        <span>Bring in past bets instead of starting from zero.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-trust-pill">
        <strong>Private betting history</strong>
        <span>Your bets, notes, and results stay in one private account.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-trust-pill">
        <strong>Track cash movement</strong>
        <span>Deposits and withdrawals live beside betting results.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-trust-pill">
        <strong>Keep the workflow within reach</strong>
        <span>Log bets and check your numbers on desktop or mobile.</span>
      </div>
