  <section id="features" class="landing-section-heading">
    <p class="eyebrow">Core workflow</p>
    <h2>Three jobs. One clean routine.</h2>
    <p>Log the wager, read the bankroll, and review performance clearly enough to make a better next decision.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="feature-grid landing-features landing-features-premium">
    <article class="card feature-card feature-card-highlight feature-card-premium">
      <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">Track</div>
      <p class="feature-kicker">Track the bet</p>
      <h3>Keep the full wager history in one place.</h3>
      <p>Log it once while the details are fresh. Stop rebuilding it later.</p>
      <ul class="feature-list checked-list">
        <li>Odds, stake, result, and notes stay together</li>
        <li>Fast entry for daily use</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
    <article class="card feature-card feature-card-highlight feature-card-premium">
