    </article>
    <article class="card feature-card feature-card-highlight feature-card-premium">
      <div class="feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">Manage</div>
      <p class="feature-kicker">Manage bankroll</p>
      <h3>Keep bankroll discipline in view.</h3>
      <p>See bankroll movement, drawdown, and unit sizing together over time.</p>
      <ul class="feature-list checked-list">
        <li>Monitor drawdown before it gets ignored</li>
        <li>Keep stake sizing accountable</li>
